main event: A bright, white to yellow object was observed in the sky for over 2 minutes, moving at a constant rate of speed and rapidly moving away.
interesting points: The object was described as 12 times larger than a star.
The object changed color from white to bright yellow.
The object was observed at an estimated altitude of 35,000 feet.
The object was seen again one week later by five people.
The object was observed for a total of 5 minutes.
sighted object: a bright, white to yellow object
